properties.description: string that username starts with, or an empty string to return all members

properties.name: limit
properties.description: maximum number of members to send matching the query ; a limit of 0 can be used with an empty string query to return all members

properties.description: used to specify if we want the presences of the matched members

properties.description: all thread member objects from the synced threads for the current user, indicating which threads the current user has been added to
